Skills.Name: Phantom Strike
Skills.Description: Inflicts <code=400,param=256><color=#3398f1>Weakness</color> ({0}% of skill user's ATK) on all enemies for 10s. Also cancels all <code=200,param=115><color=#3398f1>Shield</color> effects. Also cancels 3x Buff effects. Also inflicts 2-hit DMG (<color=red>{3}%</color> + <color=red>{4}%</color>). Further raises DMG Received by <color=red>{5}%</color> for 10s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts Weakness, cancels Shield and Buff effect(s), inflicts 2-hit DMG and raises DMG Received for all enemies
